{"id": 2478, "genre": 1001, "title": "你在什么时候会觉得一个人“对真实世界一无所知”？", "description": "来分享你听过的当代版“何不食肉糜”型发言。（题图来自：iStock ©️ George Peters）", "record_count": 3934, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20180718154652DP2yXd9rGReWJA4j.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-08-03T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 297228, "content": "以前不知道燕尾夹，被领导嫌弃并大声骂了一次，记忆深刻。那时感觉自己对好多东西都没有认知。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1427203}, {"id": 297231, "content": "有钱可以为所欲为", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 991726}, {"id": 297233, "content": "“我老公说他一定会改的，嗯，我相信他！٩(•̤̀ᵕ•̤́๑)ᵒᵏ”", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1428403}, {"id": 298769, "content": "原来我喜欢的他也只是一个普通人", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1441309}, {"id": 298003, "content": "说的都是各自的真实世界", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1431999}, {"id": 298259, "content": "当我刚刚开始工作的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1087262}, {"id": 297495, "content": "上大学😅", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1431143}, {"id": 298007, "content": "每当我被骗的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1277688}, {"id": 297240, "content": "人不犯我 我不犯人", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1293918}, {"id": 297499, "content": "有一个“真实世界”吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1374024}, {"id": 305691, "content": "刚回国就发现一大堆统一的自行车", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1477039}, {"id": 297244, "content": "当我第一次进入一个白领、书虫、老司机的开车（黄色内容）的微信群后，突然发现我对这个世界真的是一无所知。原来微信还能这么用。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1428530}, {"id": 299292, "content": "有人觉得同性恋是种病🙃", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1446132}, {"id": 297501, "content": "认识到某组.织真实的面目和套路", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1431414}, {"id": 305693, "content": "老外找零钱时给他整的加零的，他会发疯", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1477039}, {"id": 297502, "content": "被骗了60多年。才知道真相。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1431445}, {"id": 297503, "content": "莫名其妙被小部分人带表了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1431445}, {"id": 297252, "content": "为赋新词强说愁。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1419933}, {"id": 297258, "content": "下一次吧。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1407519}, {"id": 297772, "content": "世界上怎么会有抑郁症", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1434081}, {"id": 293170, "content": "问毕业的学妹说房子租好了吗，对方说，“还没呢，不着急，租房软件上看到有很多性价比还不错的”", "image": null, "praise_count": 244, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 293171, "content": "零基础的朋友说打算做游戏设计师，并且觉得自己小时候学过点素描就算有经验基础", "image": null, "praise_count": 112, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 293172, "content": "看到刚高考完觉得人生解放未来一片坦途的孩子们", "image": null, "praise_count": 776, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 297273, "content": "什么时候都觉得。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1091141}, {"id": 297533, "content": "上大学后大家都不那么重视成绩了", "image": "img/option/option/20180906091835blX85haJAMQjiypd.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1431915}, {"id": 297534, "content": "学设计只要天马行空的发挥想象力就好了", "image": "img/option/option/20180906092016HtcgELnw6i7kYGFN.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1431915}, {"id": 297284, "content": "任何时候，也包括我自己，顺便说一句，欢迎回来，想你了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1106176}, {"id": 297289, "content": "就是现在\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1429104}, {"id": 297291, "content": "在经受学校 老师的教育后刚踏入社会时", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1429175}, {"id": 296782, "content": "为什么会有抑郁症，世界这么美好，怎么会不开心呢？", "image": null, "praise_count": 347, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1212635}, {"id": 296783, "content": "看到喜欢的女孩，还羞羞怯怯，想着能够默默地看着她就好了的娃", "image": null, "praise_count": 74, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1408231}, {"id": 296785, "content": "我相信房价一定会跌的，根据xxx的经济理论和经济规律，以及参照xxx国家的历史来看，房价泡沫就会在未来十几年内破灭，现在买房不划算", "image": null, "praise_count": 230, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1426174}, {"id": 296786, "content": "大學同學說將來要買大房子。（座標香港）", "image": null, "praise_count": 27, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1387536}, {"id": 352339, "content": "我每时每刻都觉得自己如此", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1379219}, {"id": 296787, "content": "出国留学就一定会轻轻松松而且前途光明", "image": null, "praise_count": 139, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1380281}, {"id": 296788, "content": "你出过国吗？你在外国半夜出门试试？", "image": null, "praise_count": 95, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 535937}, {"id": 296789, "content": "我打算做游戏设计师，素描也没有学过", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 927309}, {"id": 296790, "content": "现在", "image": null, "praise_count": 26, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 602753}, {"id": 297302, "content": "每天都会看到新的东西，感觉自己永远也不会聪明。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1175999}, {"id": 296791, "content": "股票下跌的时候，怀疑整个世界", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 938150}, {"id": 296792, "content": "时时刻刻，因为太过魔幻。", "image": null, "praise_count": 43, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 599749}, {"id": 297304, "content": "对世界一无所知 难道不是常态吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1378583}, {"id": 296793, "content": "忙完这一阵子就可以休息了", "image": null, "praise_count": 186, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1335396}, {"id": 297305, "content": "还相信水能载舟，亦能覆舟。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1429427}, {"id": 298073, "content": "当我们在这个互联网时代，被媒体包围的时候，所有我们知道的真相都是媒体想让我们知道的真相而已", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1437249}, {"id": 296794, "content": "相信自己的专业只要学精就能有好的前程", "image": null, "praise_count": 73, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1426197}, {"id": 296796, "content": "当你吃穿用都靠家里的时候，当你觉得工资少点无所谓反正不差那几块钱，当你还健康的时候，很多。", "image": null, "praise_count": 71, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1412411}, {"id": 296797, "content": "对各种速成教材深信不疑的众人。", "image": null, "praise_count": 23, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 408569}, {"id": 296798, "content": "还有当你觉得还年轻的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1412411}, {"id": 296799, "content": "每次妹子表达出对美好婚姻生活的电视偶像剧畅想，我都觉得妹子想多了", "image": null, "praise_count": 43, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 609045}]}